USER MANAGEMENT

LDAPS == for HTTPS secure way access by using certificate manager

then we have to create files like 
base.ldif == what action we have to create like users groups 
users.ldif == user name ans pass
groups.ldif == groups 

then go to jenkins manage jenkins security - select LDAPS - add ip of ldaps or jenins server - add groups - appy proper permission like read view build logs view 


